name: where_did_they_go_01
description: An alien from the planet Irk named Zim is sent on a secret mission to conquer Earth, not realizing that his leaders were just trying to get rid of him. There, Zim succeeds in his plans by pretending to be a child. After he failed in his mission, he had to return to his home planet. Zim never returned to his old home and now wanders through caves and grottos looking for crystals.
